comments: LAR shows Green (GSW) jumps to the side of Williams (LAC), who creates the marginal contact before releasing the pass.
Green (GSW) makes contact to the arm and body of Williams (LAC) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Williams (LAC) briefly engages and disengages with Thompson (GSW) off ball.
Durant (GSW) is not established in a screening position in Shamet's (LAC) path and he delivers contact with his backside that affects Shamet's ability to defend the play.
Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Thompson (GSW) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Shamet (LAC) places a hand/arm to the front of Curry (GSW) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Curry (GSW) makes marginal contact with Shamet (LAC) off ball when he disengages.
Iguodala (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Shamet (LAC) and does not deliver contact.
Williams (LAC) releases from the contact and does not extend his arm into Thompson (GSW) and dislodge him from his defensive position.
Williams (LAC) is established in a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Curry (GSW) on the perimeter.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Harrell (LAC) attempting to retrieve the rebound.
Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Thompson (GSW) and makes marginal arm contact.
Curry (GSW) makes marginal contact with Shamet (LAC) off ball that does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] RAR shows Curry (GSW) slides his pivot foot before the jump shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC) makes incidental contact with Green (GSW) that does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Looney (GSW) briefly grasps Gallinari's (LAC) arm but does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Looney (GSW) commits a take foul on Harrell (LAC).
Thompson (GSW) and Shamet (LAC) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
